snippet.textDisplay: Given the implications that Doom Slayer is the same character as the OG Doomguy, it's entirely possible that this murderous, unstoppable, literally-more-apocalyptic-than-the-actual-biblical-Apocalypse rampage was all brought about because some stupid demon killed his rabbit. So basically, the loss of one cute little bunny lead to the extermination of Heaven and Hell in their entirety. It's like the Butterfly Effect but more metal.
